-- Lions Name Team to Face Australia in Series-Opening Rugby Test
-- B y   D a n   B a y n e s
-- 2013-06-20T02:13:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-20/lions-name-team-to-face-australia-in-series-opening-rugby-test.html
The British and Irish Lions named
the following team to play Australia in their June 22 series-opening rugby Test at Brisbane’s Suncorp Stadium:  BRITISH AND IRISH LIONS: Leigh Halfpenny, Alex Cuthbert,
 Brian O’Driscoll , Jonathan Davies, George North, Jonathan
Sexton, Mike Phillips, Jamie Heaslip, Sam Warburton (captain),
Tom Croft, Paul O’Connell, Alun Wyn Jones, Adam Jones, Tom
Youngs, Alex Corbisiero.  Replacements: Richard Hibbard, Mako Vunipola, Dan Cole,
Geoff Parling, Dan Lydiate, Ben Youngs, Owen Farrell, Sean
Maitland.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Baynes at 
 dbaynes@bloomberg.net  